  <name>Gautier RSS</name>
  <summary>Show listings from Internet sites</summary>
  <description>
    <p>RSS/Atom Reader</p>
    <p>Shows Internet feeds in a clean and obvious way. Comes with a screen that helps you add new feeds or purge those you no longer need.</p>
    <p>The program uses a native code UI that runs smooth with no bloat.</p>
    <p>Considerations</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Feed providers prefer their site is accessed no earlier than once per hour.</li>
      <li>The program respects those conditions by default.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
